1. *Informacija* o stanju u zemlji je dostupna svima. (Information about the situation in the country is available to everyone.)

2. On je obavestio javnost o novim *informacijama*. (He informed the public about new information.)

3. Ova agencija se bavi prikupljanjem *informacija*. (This agency deals with the collection of information.)

4. *Informacije* o vremenskim uslovima se mogu naći na internetu. (Information about the weather conditions can be found on the internet.)

5. Ona je prešla u drugu firmu zbog boljih *informacija*. (She changed to another company due to better information.)